Terms and Conditions

Terms and Conditions

In case of any questions, contact us directly on contact@nathanfx.com email address or on https://t.me/+ykp8HWnzE1YxZDA8 Telegram Communicator. 

  • Subscription fee will automatically be charged, depending on chosen package by Customer. Payment method will be charged at the end of each service period, unless Customer decides to cancel subscription for the nathanfx services. 
  • Customer can unsubscribe to the nathanfx service at anytime, then the next fee will not be charged. To cancel subscription, Customer has to log in to Customer’s  account on this website (https://nathanfx/my-account/sumo-subscriptions) go to  „MY SUBSCRIPTIONS”, choose the subscription and click „CANCEL”. After the subscription is cancelled, the Customer will receive a confirmation email on the registered email address.  

In case of any problems, contact us on contact@nathanfx.com email address or on https://t.me/+ykp8HWnzE1YxZDA8 Telegram Communicator. 

  • The nathanfx service is provided via group on Telegram Communicator/on Nathan FX.com website/via email.  
  • After purchasing nathanfx service, Customer will receive an email with a joining link which gives access to purchased service.  
  • The information on this website and group on Telegram Communicator is not intended for distribution. Anybody found distributing will be immediately removed from the services. 
  • RR Group is not responsible for any losses suffered by Customer. Our service and all content is provided for educational purposes only and should not be considered as a solicitation to buy or to sell.  
  • Customer can ask for a money refund within 14 days after purchasing the nathanfx service. Customer needs to write a request, via the contact form on this website.  (https://nathanfx/#contact) with the reason and order number. Request will be considered within 3 working days and Customer will be informed vie email after the refund is proceeded. From refunded amount, refund fees may be deducted. 

After the refund is proceeded, Customer access to nathanfx service is blocked.  

  • RR Group undertakes, for Customer who purchased the Life-me Subscription, to provide service for the minimum of 24 months.  
  • RR Group is under Polish jurisdiction. Any disputes regarding this website, its content or services will be brought only in the Polish courts. 
  • In certain circumstances, nathanfx services can be temporality suspended. 
  • Our Privacy Policy can be found here. 
  • Our Fulfilment policy can be found here. 
  • We have the right to terminate Customer use of this website if we determine in our sole discretion that you have breached the terms and conditions. 
  • After purchasing any nathanfx service, Customer accept all the above conditions.  RR Group, address: Dabrowskiego 77a, Poznan 60-529, PL
